      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Your knowledge of gymnastics tricks and martial arts techniques remove some of the disadvantages of charging your enemies.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Acrobatics 3 ranks</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> As part of the action to make a charge attack, you can attempt an @Check[type:acrobatics] with a DC of 15 plus 1-1/2 times the CR of the creature you are charging. If you succeed at this check, you can halve either the –2 penalty to attack or the –2 penalty to AC from charging.</p>"
